* Improved {{docmod|galaktos}}-based audio visualizations on FreeBSD 
* Miscellaneous bugfixes in multiple modules and in [[libvlc]] ({{docmod|transcode}} stream output, OSD menu video filter, [[Documentation:Modules/vcd|VCD]] input, [[Documentation:Modules/sap|SAP]] services discovery, {{docmod|http}} control interface)
